title: Whitehall's Ivanna Jones is lehighvalleylive Girls Soccer Player of Week
text:
Ivanna Jones , Whitehall 
The senior forward has scored two goals in three of Whitehall's last four games. 
Jones scored twice in the Zephyrs' 3-1 win over Emmaus on Monday, she had both goals in a 2-0 win over Easton on Saturday and had two more in a 3-1 win over Nazareth last Tuesday. 
In the only game she didn't have two goals, Jones tallied the only score in a 1-0 win over Northampton on Thursday. 
Jones has 21 goals on the season. 
Honorable mention: Fr. F Mikayla Bates , Notre Dame; Jr. D. Cassie Kelly , Notre Dame; Jr. F Olivia Askerneese , Liberty; Sophia Benes , Northampton; Jr. M Ava Markle , Freedom; Sr. F. Amy Strauser , Nazareth; So. Amanda Mobley , Southern Lehigh; Sr. F Paige Jones , Saucon Valley; Gaby Vega , Wilson; Sr. Haley Vavrek , Voorhees.
